php sever tili htmlga oxwap faylga bossa ocmoqci bosa sayt iwlamidi sayt iwlawi uchun server iwga tuwuwi kere 
php fayl index.php shunday .php bilan yaratilinadi php faylda html kod muamosiz bemalol iwlidi

<?php
    echo "hello world";
    echo "dasdasdasd"
?>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
</body>
</html>

php kod yoziw uchun <?php mawi teg ochiladi ?> bunda yopiladi va wu tegni ichidigi hamma kod iwlidi agar wu tegdan tawqarida bolsa kod
iwlamidi.
